reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Efficient and Stylish Dishwasher Magnet
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Dishwasher Magnet Clean Dirty Sign Shutter, and it has proven to be a game-changer in my kitchen. The sleek design seamlessly blends with my dishwasher, adding a touch of sophistication.The shutter mechanism is not only practical but also easy to use – a simple flick switches the sign from clean to dirty and vice versa. This feature has been a lifesaver in our busy household, ensuring no more confusion about the status of the dishes.

reviews.reviewText: If you purchase this, you'll never need to wonder if the dishes are clean or dirty.This product is well made, is magnetic, and easily moves from dirty to clean.We use it multiple times a day and have had no issues!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Adheres instantly, remains adhered until moved, easily slides between large font clean and dirty positions. Consistent with expensive stainless steel dishwasher.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This magnet is large and it's excellent. You can read it from anywhere in the kitchen.It doesn't stay perfectly in place with the magnets if you're sliding between clean and dirty, but it does stay put when opening and closing the dishwasher, which is arguably what matters. It did come with the adhesive stickers, but I won't be using that since it'd be a pain to clean.Now if only I could get members of the household to actually put their dishes in the dishwasher when they see the bright red Dirty sign is active. There's really no winning around here

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good sign, but weak magnet
reviews.reviewText: This is a good dishwasher "clean/dirty" sign. It seems well made, and even "clicks" into place at either end of the slide to prevent sliding due to vibration as the dishwasher runs.However, the magnet is extremely weak. It won't hold the sign from moving around on the front of the dishwasher when the slide is slid back and forth.Also, the magnet doesn't hold the sign on the dishwasher door when the door is opened. It falls off onto the floor about half the time.The adhesives must be used to keep the sign on the dishwasher door.

reviews.reviewTitle: Works well and has definitely improved relations within the fam ;)
reviews.reviewText: Only little niggle is that this gadget is flat, and our dishwasher has a slightly curved surface so it can be tricky to get it to grip well. Other than that it does exactly what it's supposed to.

The media could not be loaded. I got fed up with everyone in the house always asking if the load is clean or dirty before they open the dishwasher so this is very helpful. I recommend this to everyone who uses dishwashers. Once the cycle is started flip the switch to clean so once it ends, the next person will know they are clean. Once all the load is removed, that person should flip to “Dirty” since it’s now empty anything you put inside will be dirty. Cool system to have.
